detaileddescription.para: The class fullvert The class defining a vertex with full channel decomposition i.e. irreducible (bare) a, p and t channels The fullvert in the standard configuration is the full vertex \Gamma with all components (only_same_channel=false and Ir=false) for Ir = true it is an r-irreducible vertex I_r (r is the channel of the bubble) for only_same_channel it only contains the r-reducible component
